  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Dorne.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Dorne and the location of the Salt Shore\"><img alt=\"Dorne and the location of the Salt Shore\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f5/Dorne.png/400px-Dorne.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"191\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f5/Dorne.png/600px-Dorne.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f5/Dorne.png/800px-Dorne.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 83.3%; left: 67.5%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -5px; top: -5px; width: 10px; font-size: 10px;\"><img alt=\"Dorne and the location of the Salt Shore\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/10px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Salt Shore\" width=\"10\" height=\"10\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/15px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/20px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size: 80%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; top:-0.15em; left: -3em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\"><b>Salt Shore</b></span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\"><a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a> and the location of the Salt Shore\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><table>\n\n<tbody><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Salt Shore</b> is the seat of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Gargalen\" title=\"House Gargalen\">House Gargalen</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a>. It lies on the southern coast along the <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Sea\" title=\"Summer Sea\">Summer Sea</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Salt_Shore&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>While sailing to the <a href=\"/index.php/Sunset_Sea\" title=\"Sunset Sea\">Sunset Sea</a>, the fleet of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Alyn_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyn Velaryon\">Alyn Velaryon</a> was struck by a sudden storm as it passed the drylands west of Salt Shore.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Salt_Shore&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Map_of_the_South\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Map of the South\">Map of the South</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Under the Regents - The Voyage of Alyn Oakenfist.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible uncollapsed navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Region_Dorne\" title=\"Template:Region Dorne\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Region_Dorne&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:Region Dorne (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:Region_Dorne&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a></div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Settlements</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Blackmont\" title=\"Blackmont\">Blackmont</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ghaston_Grey\" title=\"Ghaston Grey\">Ghaston Grey</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ghost